{"tid":2227264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘭桂坊中秋長假未見人潮 蘇豪區拉騎呢橙帶劃禁區阻聚集","createTime":"2020-10-02T15:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T16:39:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88eeb2a26ed33e5d8190005f23abdfbbabfdd606","tid":2227264,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n6I-Pqxin_xN0L_cjK7JNQe3KkA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJZ5VTOOKJEKFBEBPSOWP6ZC5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn6I-Pqxin_xN0L_cjK7JNQe3KkA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJZ5VTOOKJEKFBEBPSOWP6ZC5Y.jpg&h=8ae6a69d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DCb5zHVCnLWSI4jNblig3LK07JE=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TOODAVJTJ5ABTC4X7YP6HXL6SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDCb5zHVCnLWSI4jNblig3LK07JE%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTOODAVJTJ5ABTC4X7YP6HXL6SY.jpg&h=c4a536ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/14LxbBDjBWNsskyhpggpuO_UPYY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WJHLUWDAEZFQ7INPFHURB36NS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F14LxbBDjBWNsskyhpggpuO_UPYY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWJHLUWDAEZFQ7INPFHURB36NS4.jpg&h=a17c8d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於酒吧林立的蘇豪區卑利街明顯較多市民超過4人聚集，警方以雪糕桶和橙色膠帶劃出一遍禁區，意圖阻止酒吧客人在街上聚集，但未見成效，其中一間酒吧外聚了逾10名酒客，部分人更站入橙帶範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n在蘭桂坊開業7年的酒吧Rula Live經理Lila指，生意由去年社會運動開始轉差，今年疫情以來生意估計大跌九成，第一波疫情時因沒有強制酒吧停業還能維持營運，二三波之後客人已近乎全部流失，因為酒吧一般都營業至凌晨4、5點，現時午夜後就要停業好難做生意，她認為酒吧限桌令其實可以放寬到與食肆人數睇齊，4個甚至6個一檯，「你見地鐵也有很多市民緊貼住陌生人搭車。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/TU2BXJRPWRGJJIISZJAHJKAWN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FTU2BXJRPWRGJJIISZJAHJKAWN4%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=945775c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FTU2BXJRPWRGJJIISZJAHJKAWN4%2F&h=fb65a96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/TU2BXJRPWRGJJIISZJAHJKAWN4/</a>"},{"pid":"954cf75800a2edb8e52e3ff18967fcaa3df33a60","tid":2227264,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88eeb2a26ed33e5d8190005f23abdfbbabfdd606","tid":2227264,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n6I-Pqxin_xN0L_cjK7JNQe3KkA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJZ5VTOOKJEKFBEBPSOWP6ZC5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn6I-Pqxin_xN0L_cjK7JNQe3KkA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJZ5VTOOKJEKFBEBPSOWP6ZC5Y.jpg&h=8ae6a69d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DCb5zHVCnLWSI4jNblig3LK07JE=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TOODAVJTJ5ABTC4X7YP6HXL6SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDCb5zHVCnLWSI4jNblig3LK07JE%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTOODAVJTJ5ABTC4X7YP6HXL6SY.jpg&h=c4a536ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer